data.description: This picture perfect farm-type house can be your family's haven in Grand Bay. Wake up smiling with the open floor plan. High ceilings. Care-free flooring. Great colors! SS appliances will remain in the spacious kitchen; bay window in breakfast area. Huge bonus room upstairs. Front and back porches for the rockers and swingers! Recharge your batteries out by the pool or on the pool-side deck--relaxing or entertaining. Lots of pecan trees on this 1.5 acres. As a crow flies, only 15 minutes to Mississippi and 25 minutes to downtown Mobile.
